title: Episode 9 - Tana Mongeau
description:
Dave and Josh welcome Tana Mongeau to the program to talk about her long list of influencer relationships, including an attempted DM slide to Dave himself. Josh reacts to the latest song written about him. Dave retells the story of the MHOC, and considers Josh as a new potential member.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/bffspod
